      "value": "<p>The armorist may cause a piece of summoned or bound equipment to appear on or in the possession of a Conjuration sphere companion that she has summoned. The companion must be within 25 feet + 5 feet per two armorist levels. The companion may be treated as the armorist for the purposes of maintaining the bound equipment in its possession.</p>\n<p>Additionally, if she possesses the Variable Armaments feat, she may apply the benefits of any equipment tricks granting additional weapon special ability options to those available to her companion.</p>\n",
